name: Laws of Karma — #5 Law of Responsibility
description:
Did you know that you're the product of your decisions? Whatever paths you choose, emotion you hold, or words you say will lead you somewhere.

As portrayed in this artwork, this celestial gang choose to have a speedy ride towards the unknown future. Whatever happens next, they're prepared to face it. So I hope this artwork could be a gentle reminder for us all, to be responsible towards the choices we made.
